{"about_the_game":"&quot;Pomberito&quot; is a first-person horror adventure game set in the folklore-rich landscapes of South America. The game unfolds over five micro-episodes, each representing a night from Monday to Friday. Taking place in the rural countryside of a northeastern province of Argentina, players step into the shoes of a local character tasked with completing daily chores in a farm.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761100/extras/21.jpg?t=1734836150\" /><br><br>As the protagonist navigates through the isolated environment, you will encounter elements inspired by South American folklore, adding a unique and cultural twist to the horror genre. The game's suspenseful ambiance intensifies as each night progresses, with unexpected twists and encounters awaiting the player.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761100/extras/13.jpg?t=1734836150\" /><br><br>One of the standout features of &quot;Pomberito&quot; is its multiple endings, allowing players to explore different outcomes based on their decisions and actions throughout the week. Players will strive to uncover the mysteries surrounding the folklore-inspired horrors in the rural landscapes of Argentina.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2761100/extras/12.jpg?t=1734836150\" />","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Catrasca","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2761100/d17155d7fe42d9e746f339bc16d2d2ac7fe924c0.jpg"},{"name":"Luz Mala","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2761100/060a2e2d5729160ca613a69dc2c7853ea89ee37e.jpg"},{"name":"Fuego","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2761100/6ce0cf487d1cf026bdadadd6e3b58d120b58cf95.jpg"},{"name":"Pomberito","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamst